Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:16.51,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Suddenly we met \NWhile just passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:25.31,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Thanks to cars going around back and forth \NWith their headlights on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:28.40,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Chances are your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.65,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Gave you a cold shower
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.66,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,When remembering those times today,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:41.04,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,I don't feel like myself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:49.53,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Ah once upon a time \NNot a single of those faces was around
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:59.01,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,But you were so hurt, \NYou didn't want to see them anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:03.77,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Thank you for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:11.36,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Every time we meet somewhere, \NWe have to part again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:15.86,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Not a single of your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:18.99,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Not even your beloved one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:30.00,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Will ever wish to return to those times. \NYou know it, don't you, love?
